  <brief_title>Long Term Prophylactic Therapy of Congenital Long QT Syndrome Type III (LQT3) With Ranolazine</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Tel-Aviv Sourasky Medical Center</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Tel-Aviv Sourasky Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether ranolazine will reduce the risk of
      arrhythmic events in patients with long QT syndrome type 3.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
